[Course_Description]
Learn how to use Windows Admin Center, a locally deployed browser-based app, to manage PCs, servers, clients, virtual machines, clusters, and hyper-converged infrastructure. This course shows how to install and use Windows Admin Center to perform system administration from any location with an internet connection. Robert McMillen provides a tour of the interface and demonstrates how to complete common tasks. He covers firewall and DNS setup, server administration, client management, Azure resource management, cluster management, and more.